snippet.title: The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild - DLC Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
Take on the Trial of the Sword in The Legend of Zelda: Breath of the Wild DLC Pack 1, out 30/06 on Nintendo Switch and Wii U. DLC Pack 2 arrives in winter.
